<br>
Ideally, you will not cast at target-X until you know you have enough mana to stand through the remainder of the fight with target-X. <br>
<br>
If you're going to have to get agro to keep up with your mana regen, and preferably not take damage due to skins, then the pattern would be like:  Med until you can start nuking and you have enough mana to finish the kill.  Stand close enough for target-X to hit you, but farther from target-X than the tank.  Begin nuking, possibly using concussion if you have it, and don't stop.<br>
